'''Mackenzie''' (2005-2025) was an American Tabby cat who lives in a loving life in Baltimore, Maryland and mother of 10 kittens

== Biography ==

=== First birth ===
Mackenzie was born in a home as an result she slid right out of his mother and onto the cozy warm blanket in home. Mackenzie seems nice to live, his owner named Aisha Mountjoy an Grocery

== Life ==
When Mackenzie was 3 months old, His Owner adopted an Persian cat named Percival. 6 months later His owner married Lorenzo Thomas , she changed her name into Aisha Thomas,

In 2006 she went into heat, she mated with Percival the cat, She gave to 3 kittens but sadly one of her kittens was died shortly after birth, But his owner gived her kitten Sassy to someone else who offered more stable home

In 2007 she mated Percival the cat again, and didn't give birth, 9 months, She diagnosed with roundworms

In 2008 His owner Aisha took Mackenzie in The vet, Aisha agreed to pay for her treatment

In 2012 she practiced giving kiss, Aisha gave birth an baby named Syklar Thomas

In 2022 Mackenzie diagnosed with FIV, She tasted blood in his mouth after eating

2025, Aisha took him to the vet, The vet wanted to euthanaise Mackenzie she showed final moments of Aisha

